電，不過提醒還是要慎防營業秘密外流的可能。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"96e4c0317d2dc6059232a133969371ab893b7b5a","tid":2154363,"uid":114946,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T06:08:00.000Z","msg":"有實力嘅人去邊都俾人挖架啦。資本社會係咁<br />\n中國啲企業到宜家都會挖香港人去中國或者進軍香港，不過間公司上軌道之後就炒咁解。"},{"pid":"fc5da4510d1fc0cf1e488776c636247c2aa3c234","tid":2154363,"uid":177313,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"78a175bc89fb26f5ecd7ea55f3fb295926e3f487","tid":2154363,"uid":30067,"like":261,"dislike":0,"score":261,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"唔係搵錯人<br />\n係搵唔齊人<br />\n因為分工細"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T06:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U4zVKkh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU4zVKkh.png&h=a95fb85d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"369504bceced0a77ed0a79b27077fbaaf3260980","tid":2154363,"uid":550,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T06:13:57.000Z","msg":"佢係講緊挖唔齊人 唔係唔啱人<br />\n即係等於亞視挖到肥蛆、何B同鵬哥過檔<br />\n但無挖到幕後編審嗰班人"},{"pid":"c4f16f9e3d422879d0b681c2efbf808b613b1767","tid":2154363,"uid":131884,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"c4c0849b484098717902f08a342e7d0229b5b1e9","tid":2154363,"uid":53209,"like":130,"dislike":2,"score":128,"quote":{"pid":"90a05434e57ae95f1563ef1a2f8c87e4c044d65c","tid":2154363,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:38:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200813/1783522.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200813%2F1783522.htm&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzmINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=d9f38271\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200813/1783522.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n咁都可以攪錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:59:37.000Z","msg":